{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Here is your **professional, developer-ready Hero Banner Section prompt** (Shopify/Liquid compatible structure):
    
    ---
    
    # ✅ Advanced Hero Banner Section – Customizable Slider
    
    ## 🎯 Objective
    
    Create a fully customizable **Hero Banner Section** with dynamic image slider functionality, advanced layout controls, overlay settings, and mobile responsiveness.
    
    ---
    
    # 1️⃣ Image Settings
    
    ### 🖼 Multiple Image Upload
    
    * Allow adding **4–5 images (dynamic blocks)**
    * If **more than 1 image** → Enable Slider
    * If **only 1 image** → Slider disabled automatically (no arrows, dots, autoplay)
    
    ### Image Display
    
    * Image as **Background Image**
    * Background size option:
    
      * Cover
      * Contain
    * Background position control:
    
      * Center
      * Top
      * Bottom
      * Left
      * Right
    
    ### Section Height Control
    
    * Custom height setting (px / vh)
    * Mobile height separate control
    
    ---
    
    # 2️⃣ Slider Settings (Only if enabled)
    
    Show these settings **only if image count > 1**
    
    * Show/Hide:
    
      * Dots
      * Arrows
      * Counter (1/5 type)
    * Autoplay toggle
    * Autoplay speed (ms)
    * Infinite loop toggle
    * Pause on hover toggle
    
    ---
    
    # 3️⃣ Overlay Settings
    
    ### Overlay Controls
    
    * Overlay Color picker
    * Overlay Opacity (0 – 100%)
    * Overlay Blend Mode option
    * Mask Overlay Style (CSS mask based)
    
      * Gradient mask
      * Shape mask
      * Custom mask strength control
    
    Overlay must sit above image but below text.
    
    ---
    
    # 4️⃣ Text Content Settings
    
    ### Conditional Rendering (Liquid Logic)
    
    * If text field is blank → do not render element
    * No empty spacing if content is empty
    
    Example logic requirement:
    
    ```
    {% if section.settings.heading != blank %}
      <h2>{{ section.settings.heading }}</h2>
    {% endif %}
    ```
    
    ---
    
    # 5️⃣ Text Structure
    
    ### 🏷 Small Title (with SVG icon)
    
    * SVG upload option
    * Title font size fixed or adjustable (default 16px)
    * Spacing below title control
    
    ### 📝 Heading
    
    * H1 / H2 selectable
    * Font size control (responsive)
    * Letter spacing option
    * Bottom spacing control
    
    ### 📄 Rich Text
    
    * Editable rich text area
    * Line height control
    * Max width control
    
    ---
    
    # 6️⃣ Buttons (2 Buttons)
    
    For each button:
    
    * Enable/Disable toggle
    * Button label
    * Button link
    * Button style (Primary / Secondary / Outline)
    * Open in new tab option
    
    If button text blank → button hidden automatically.
    
    ---
    
    # 7️⃣ Text Alignment & Position Controls
    
    ### Text Alignment
    
    * Left
    * Center
    * Right
    
    ### Content Position Over Image
    
    * Top Left
    * Top Center
    * Top Right
    * Center Left
    * Center
    * Center Right
    * Bottom Left
    * Bottom Center
    * Bottom Right
    
    ### Content Width Control
    
    * Full width
    * Container width
    * Custom max width (px)
    
    ### Content Padding Controls
    
    * Top padding
    * Bottom padding
    * Left padding
    * Right padding
    
    ---
    
    # 8️⃣ Layout Control
    
    Option:
    
    * Text full width over banner
    * Text inside centered container
    
    ---
    
    # 9️⃣ Mobile Responsive Behavior
    
    ### Mobile Specific Settings
    
    * Separate text alignment for mobile
    * Separate font sizes
    * Separate height control
    
    ### Mobile Layout
    
    * Option:
    
      * Text over image (default)
      * Image top + Text below with background color
    
    If “Text below image” selected:
    
    * Background color picker for text area
    * Padding control for mobile text area
    
    ---
    
    # 🔟 Accessibility & Performance
    
    * Alt text required for images
    * Proper heading hierarchy
    * Lazy loading enabled
    * Optimized responsive images
    * Keyboard accessible slider controls
    
    ---
    
    # 🎨 Design Requirements
    
    * Clean vertical rhythm
    * No layout shift
    * Smooth transitions
    * Mobile-first CSS structure
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}
{% assign image_count = 0 %}
{% for i in (1..5) %}
  {% assign image_key = 'image_' | append: i %}
  {% if block.settings[image_key] != blank %}
    {% assign image_count = image_count | plus: 1 %}
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% assign slider_enabled = false %}
{% if image_count > 1 %}
  {% assign slider_enabled = true %}
{% endif %}

{% style %}
  .ai-hero-banner-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-slider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: {{ block.settings.section_height }}px;
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-slides-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-slide-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease-in-out;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-slide-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-position: {{ block.settings.background_position }};
    background-size: {{ block.settings.background_size }};
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.overlay_color }};
    opacity: {{ block.settings.overlay_opacity | divided_by: 100.0 }};
    mix-blend-mode: {{ block.settings.overlay_blend_mode }};
    z-index: 1;
  }

  {% if block.settings.mask_overlay_enabled %}
    .ai-hero-banner-mask-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      z-index: 2;
      {% if block.settings.mask_style == 'gradient' %}
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,{{ block.settings.mask_strength | divided_by: 100.0 }}) 100%);
      {% elsif block.settings.mask_style == 'radial' %}
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,0,0,0) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,{{ block.settings.mask_strength | divided_by: 100.0 }}) 100%);
      {% elsif block.settings.mask_style == 'top_bottom' %}
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,{{ block.settings.mask_strength | divided_by: 100.0 }}) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 50%, rgba(0,0,0,{{ block.settings.mask_strength | divided_by: 100.0 }}) 100%);
      {% endif %}
    }
  {% endif %}

  .ai-hero-banner-content-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    {% if block.settings.content_position == 'top-left' %}
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    {% elsif block.settings.content_position == 'top-center' %}
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: center;
    {% elsif block.settings.content_position == 'top-right' %}
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    {% elsif block.settings.content_position == 'center-left' %}
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    {% elsif block.settings.content_position == 'center' %}
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    {% elsif block.settings.content_position == 'center-right' %}
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    {% elsif block.settings.content_position == 'bottom-left' %}
      align-items: flex-end;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    {% elsif block.settings.content_position == 'bottom-center' %}
      align-items: flex-end;
      justify-content: center;
    {% elsif block.settings.content_position == 'bottom-right' %}
      align-items: flex-end;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    {% endif %}
    padding: {{ block.settings.content_padding_top }}px {{ block.settings.content_padding_right }}px {{ block.settings.content_padding_bottom }}px {{ block.settings.content_padding_left }}px;
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    {% if block.settings.layout_style == 'container' %}
      max-width: {{ block.settings.content_max_width }}px;
    {% else %}
      width: 100%;
    {% endif %}
    text-align: {{ block.settings.text_alignment }};
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-small-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: {{ block.settings.small_title_size }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.small_title_spacing }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    {% if block.settings.text_alignment == 'center' %}
      justify-content: center;
    {% elsif block.settings.text_alignment == 'right' %}
      justify-content: flex-end;
    {% else %}
      justify-content: flex-start;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-small-title-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.small_title_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.small_title_size }}px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-small-title-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    letter-spacing: {{ block.settings.heading_letter_spacing }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.heading_spacing }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-richtext-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    line-height: {{ block.settings.richtext_line_height }};
    max-width: {{ block.settings.richtext_max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto {{ block.settings.richtext_spacing }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    {% if block.settings.text_alignment == 'center' %}
      justify-content: center;
    {% elsif block.settings.text_alignment == 'right' %}
      justify-content: flex-end;
    {% else %}
      justify-content: flex-start;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 12px 32px;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 14px;
    font-size: 14px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-button-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: #000000;
    color: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #000000;
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-button-primary-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: #333333;
    border-color: #333333;
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-button-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-button-secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-button-outline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    border: 2px solid {{ block.settings.text_color }};
  }

  .ai-hero-banner-button-outline-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    color: #000000;
  }

  {% if slider_enabled %}
    .ai-hero-banner-arrows-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      z-index: 4;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 20px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .ai-hero-banner-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      border: none;
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      pointer-events: auto;
    }

    .ai-hero-banner-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
    }

    .ai-hero-banner-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
    }

    .ai-hero-banner-dots-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 20px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      z-index: 4;
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .ai-hero-banner-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .ai-hero-banner-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
      width: 30px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .ai-hero-banner-counter-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: absolute;
      top: 20px;
      right: 20px;
      z-index: 4;
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  {% endif %}

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-hero-banner-slider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      height: {{ block.settings.mobile_section_height }}px;
    }

    {% if block.settings.mobile_layout == 'text_below' %}
      .ai-hero-banner-slider-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        height: auto;
      }

      .ai-hero-banner-slide-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .ai-hero-banner-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        position: relative;
        height: {{ block.settings.mobile_section_height }}px;
      }

      .ai-hero-banner-content-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        position: relative;
        background-color: {{ block.settings.mobile_text_bg_color }};
        padding: {{ block.settings.mobile_text_padding }}px;
        height: auto;
      }

      .ai-hero-banner-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }},
      .ai-hero-banner-mask-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
        display: none;
      }
    {% endif %}

    .ai-hero-banner-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      text-align: {{ block.settings.mobile_text_alignment }};
    }

    .ai-hero-banner-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.mobile_heading_size }}px;
    }

    .ai-hero-banner-small-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.mobile_small_title_size }}px;
      {% if block.settings.mobile_text_alignment == 'center' %}
        justify-content: center;
      {% elsif block.settings.mobile_text_alignment == 'right' %}
        justify-content: flex-end;
      {% else %}
        justify-content: flex-start;
      {% endif %}
    }

    .ai-hero-banner-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      {% if block.settings.mobile_text_alignment == 'center' %}
        justify-content: center;
      {% elsif block.settings.mobile_text_alignment == 'right' %}
        justify-content: flex-end;
      {% else %}
        justify-content: flex-start;
      {% endif %}
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<hero-banner-{{ ai_gen_id }}
  class="ai-hero-banner-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
  data-autoplay="{{ block.settings.autoplay_enabled }}"
  data-autoplay-speed="{{ block.settings.autoplay_speed }}"
  data-infinite="{{ block.settings.infinite_loop }}"
  data-pause-on-hover="{{ block.settings.pause_on_hover }}"
  {{ block.shopify_attributes }}
>
  <div class="ai-hero-banner-slider-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-hero-banner-slides-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% for i in (1..5) %}
        {% assign image_key = 'image_' | append: i %}
        {% assign image = block.settings[image_key] %}
        {% if image != blank %}
          <div class="ai-hero-banner-slide-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-slide-index="{{ forloop.index0 }}">
            <div
              class="ai-hero-banner-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              style="background-image: url('{{ image | image_url: width: 2000 }}');"
              role="img"
              aria-label="{{ image.alt | escape }}"
            ></div>

            <div class="ai-hero-banner-overlay-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>

            {% if block.settings.mask_overlay_enabled %}
              <div class="ai-hero-banner-mask-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
            {% endif %}

            <div class="ai-hero-banner-content-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-hero-banner-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {% if block.settings.small_title != blank %}
                  <div class="ai-hero-banner-small-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    {% if block.settings.small_title_icon != blank %}
                      <div class="ai-hero-banner-small-title-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                        <img
                          src="{{ block.settings.small_title_icon | image_url: width: 100 }}"
                          alt=""
                          loading="lazy"
                          width="100"
                          height="100"
                        >
                      </div>
                    {% endif %}
                    <span>{{ block.settings.small_title }}</span>
                  </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
                  {% if block.settings.heading_tag == 'h1' %}
                    <h1 class="ai-hero-banner-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h1>
                  {% else %}
                    <h2 class="ai-hero-banner-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
                  {% endif %}
                {% endif %}

                {% if block.settings.richtext != blank %}
                  <div class="ai-hero-banner-richtext-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    {{ block.settings.richtext }}
                  </div>
                {% endif %}

                {% if block.settings.button_1_enabled or block.settings.button_2_enabled %}
                  <div class="ai-hero-banner-buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                    {% if block.settings.button_1_enabled and block.settings.button_1_label != blank %}
                      <a
                        href="{{ block.settings.button_1_link }}"
                        class="ai-hero-banner-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-hero-banner-button-{{ block.settings.button_1_style }}-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                        {% if block.settings.button_1_new_tab %}target="_blank" rel="noopener"{% endif %}
                      >
                        {{ block.settings.button_1_label }}
                      </a>
                    {% endif %}

                    {% if block.settings.button_2_enabled and block.settings.button_2_label != blank %}
                      <a
                        href="{{ block.settings.button_2_link }}"
                        class="ai-hero-banner-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-hero-banner-button-{{ block.settings.button_2_style }}-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                        {% if block.settings.button_2_new_tab %}target="_blank" rel="noopener"{% endif %}
                      >
                        {{ block.settings.button_2_label }}
                      </a>
                    {% endif %}
                  </div>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    {% if slider_enabled %}
      {% if block.settings.show_arrows %}
        <div class="ai-hero-banner-arrows-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <button
            class="ai-hero-banner-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-hero-banner-prev-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            aria-label="Previous slide"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <button
            class="ai-hero-banner-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-hero-banner-next-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
            aria-label="Next slide"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.show_dots %}
        <div class="ai-hero-banner-dots-{{ ai_gen_id }}"></div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.show_counter %}
        <div class="ai-hero-banner-counter-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <span class="ai-hero-banner-current-{{ ai_gen_id }}">1</span> / <span class="ai-hero-banner-total-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ image_count }}</span>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</hero-banner-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class HeroBanner{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
        this.currentSlide = 0;
        this.slides = [];
        this.autoplayInterval = null;
        this.isHovered = false;
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.slides = Array.from(this.querySelectorAll('.ai-hero-banner-slide-{{ ai_gen_id }}'));
        this.totalSlides = this.slides.length;

        if (this.totalSlides === 0) return;

        this.slides[0].classList.add('active');

        if (this.totalSlides > 1) {
          this.setupControls();
          this.setupAutoplay();
        }
      }

      setupControls() {
        const prevBtn = this.querySelector('.ai-hero-banner-prev-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        const nextBtn = this.querySelector('.ai-hero-banner-next-{{ ai_gen_id }}');

        if (prevBtn) {
          prevBtn.addEventListener('click', () => this.prevSlide());
        }

        if (nextBtn) {
          nextBtn.addEventListener('click', () => this.nextSlide());
        }

        this.setupDots();
        this.setupKeyboard();
      }

      setupDots() {
        const dotsContainer = this.querySelector('.ai-hero-banner-dots-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        if (!dotsContainer) return;

        for (let i = 0; i < this.totalSlides; i++) {
          const dot = document.createElement('button');
          dot.classList.add('ai-hero-banner-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
          dot.setAttribute('aria-label', `Go to slide ${i + 1}`);
          if (i === 0) dot.classList.add('active');
          dot.addEventListener('click', () => this.goToSlide(i));
          dotsContainer.appendChild(dot);
        }
      }

      setupKeyboard() {
        this.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
          if (e.key === 'ArrowLeft') {
            this.prevSlide();
          } else if (e.key === 'ArrowRight') {
            this.nextSlide();
          }
        });
      }

      setupAutoplay() {
        const autoplayEnabled = this.dataset.autoplay === 'true';
        const pauseOnHover = this.dataset.pauseOnHover === 'true';

        if (!autoplayEnabled) return;

        const speed = parseInt(this.dataset.autoplaySpeed) || 5000;

        this.startAutoplay(speed);

        if (pauseOnHover) {
          this.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {
            this.isHovered = true;
            this.stopAutoplay();
          });

          this.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
            this.isHovered = false;
            this.startAutoplay(speed);
          });
        }
      }

      startAutoplay(speed) {
        this.stopAutoplay();
        this.autoplayInterval = setInterval(() => {
          if (!this.isHovered) {
            this.nextSlide();
          }
        }, speed);
      }

      stopAutoplay() {
        if (this.autoplayInterval) {
          clearInterval(this.autoplayInterval);
          this.autoplayInterval = null;
        }
      }

      goToSlide(index) {
        this.slides[this.currentSlide].classList.remove('active');

        const dots = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-hero-banner-dot-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        if (dots[this.currentSlide]) {
          dots[this.currentSlide].classList.remove('active');
        }

        this.currentSlide = index;

        this.slides[this.currentSlide].classList.add('active');
        if (dots[this.currentSlide]) {
          dots[this.currentSlide].classList.add('active');
        }

        this.updateCounter();
      }

      nextSlide() {
        const infiniteLoop = this.dataset.infinite === 'true';
        let nextIndex = this.currentSlide + 1;

        if (nextIndex >= this.totalSlides) {
          nextIndex = infiniteLoop ? 0 : this.totalSlides - 1;
        }

        this.goToSlide(nextIndex);
      }

      prevSlide() {
        const infiniteLoop = this.dataset.infinite === 'true';
        let prevIndex = this.currentSlide - 1;

        if (prevIndex < 0) {
          prevIndex = infiniteLoop ? this.totalSlides - 1 : 0;
        }

        this.goToSlide(prevIndex);
      }

      updateCounter() {
        const currentCounter = this.querySelector('.ai-hero-banner-current-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        if (currentCounter) {
          currentCounter.textContent = this.currentSlide + 1;
        }
      }

      disconnectedCallback() {
        this.stopAutoplay();
      }
    }

    customElements.define('hero-banner-{{ ai_gen_id }}', HeroBanner{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

